oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: George Jones at Aunt Minnie's Farm
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Flags; Jones, George, 1931-2013; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing George Jones with the Big John Trimble Comedy Show, Virginia Squires, Hobbs and Partners, and others at Aunt Minnie's Farm on August 20. Poster features a metal photoplate of George Jones and American flags.
